  "created": 1650620342,
  "updated": 1703404638,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "626277b6017341001d8ebbe6",
      "text": "Scrapboxのライトテーマとダークテーマをワンタッチで切り替え",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620342,
      "updated": 1650620394
    },
    {
      "id": "626277b81280f00000080b05",
      "text": "from [2022/04/22]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620342,
      "updated": 1650620342
    },
    {
      "id": "626277b81280f00000080b06",
      "text": "Scrapboxのライトテーマとダークテーマをワンタッチで切り替えたい[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620342,
      "updated": 1650620391
    },
    {
      "id": "626277b81280f00000080b07",
      "text": "　UserCSSでリンクの色とかを変えているので、それも同時に切り替わってほしい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620342,
      "updated": 1650620371
    },
    {
      "id": "626277b81280f00000080b08",
      "text": "　普段はダークテーマがいいが、[アクティブ読書]をするときにダークテーマだと白字が明るくて眩しい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620342,
      "updated": 1650620371
    },
    {
      "id": "626277f51280f00000080b0b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620403,
      "updated": 1650620403
    },
    {
      "id": "626278351280f00000080b0f",
      "text": "[prefers-color-scheme]を使って[UserCSS]を組むと切り替えられるようになります[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620467,
      "updated": 1650620550
    },
    {
      "id": "6262784c1280f00000080b11",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/8342f2d985f8161ab16ff9fd0627fccb]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620490,
      "updated": 1650620510
    },
    {
      "id": "6262efc0e5172d000053ae78",
      "text": " すごい[yosider.icon*2]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1650651073,
      "updated": 1650651074
    },
    {
      "id": "626278a11280f00000080b15",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620575,
      "updated": 1650620575
    },
    {
      "id": "626278a11280f00000080b16",
      "text": "UserScriptで切り替えたい場合",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620576,
      "updated": 1650620583
    },
    {
      "id": "6262798e1280f00000080b2e",
      "text": " 自分が使うときだけ切り替えたいならこの方がずっと楽",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620812,
      "updated": 1650620833
    },
    {
      "id": "6262f03fe5172d000053ae79",
      "text": " 　それはそうか[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1650651199,
      "updated": 1650651203
    },
    {
      "id": "626278a91280f00000080b17",
      "text": " code:script.js",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620583,
      "updated": 1650620586
    },
    {
      "id": "626278ac1280f00000080b18",
      "text": "  scrapbox.PageMenu.addItem({",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620586,
      "updated": 1650620594
    },
    {
      "id": "626278b31280f00000080b19",
      "text": "    title: \"turn color theme\",",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620594,
      "updated": 1650620610
    },
    {
      "id": "626278c41280f00000080b1b",
      "text": "    onClick: () => document.documentElement.dataset.projectTheme = ",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620610,
      "updated": 1650620760
    },
    {
      "id": "6262795b1280f00000080b22",
      "text": "      document.documentElement.dataset.projectTheme !== \"default-dark\" ?",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620761,
      "updated": 1650620762
    },
    {
      "id": "6262795a1280f00000080b21",
      "text": "        \"default-dark\" :",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620760,
      "updated": 1650620765
    },
    {
      "id": "626279601280f00000080b23",
      "text": "        \"default\",",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1650620766,
      "updated": 1650620770
    },
    {
      "id": "626278b31280f00000080b1a",
      "text": "  });",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
